        <item>
            <title>Microsoft 终止海底数据中心实验，项目至今已超过 10 年</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/25/microsoft-has-ditched-its-project-natick-underwater-data-center/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=microsoft-has-ditched-its-project-natick-underwater-data-center</link>
